"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T15:34:35.000Z","msg":"我都有n2遲啲考n1<br />\n不過有jlpt 唔等如識講<br />\nEju 同漢檢先係地獄"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T16:53:23.000Z","msg":"EJU其實易過JLPT<br />\nEJU考既其實更加係你可唔可以短時間捉到個重點<br />\n利申:EJU 卷1 45分 卷2 33X分 綜合18X分 (但最後去左野雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"4f5a29a2f5b0523c1d6c6619764d56c83d653449","tid":2478003,"uid":188436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a700ac700d9b080e9dd4e5da05e96abef6fbd131","tid":2478003,"uid":109543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"edaef84fafdd928731bc6ebe814d044f6f07cc84","tid":2478003,"uid":188436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T15:34:35.000Z","msg":"我都有n2遲啲考n1<br />\n不過有jlpt 唔等如識講<br />\nEju 同漢檢先係地獄"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T16:53:23.000Z","msg":"EJU其實易過JLPT<br />\nEJU考既其實更加係你可唔可以短時間捉到個重點<br />\n利申:EJU 卷1 45分 卷2 33X分 綜合18X分 (但最後去左野雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T17:23:46.000Z","msg":"去左邊間"},{"pid":"bb37c48809e0341c67df66e4612203f6448a8909","tid":2478003,"uid":246823,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T05:37:17.000Z","msg":"各位初學者 我會當你地係白紙一張由零開始教<br />\n今日上第一堂!!<br />\n請各位入去了解下五十音既結構先, thanks!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://ncomplex.github.io/gojuon\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fncomplex.github.io%2Fgojuon&d=8bD6%2Ff4xTvH2AAK2Q7vPtN8yddZnhMmQMHU13Um27G0%3D&h=f4b15687\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ncomplex.github.io/gojuon</a>"},{"pid":"897d6c801563ab0e719a7acae3e55191b2a37a77","tid":2478003,"uid":246823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T05:55:10.000Z","msg":"第一堂學五十音<br />\n所有日文句子都係由五十音砌出黎<br />\n<br />\n點解叫五十音 因為有五段十行<br />\n乘埋就有五十個音(部份發音唔用的 遲啲再講<br />\n<br />\n再加一個鼻音ん<br />\n<br />\n如何學習<br />\n睇上面個表 了解平仮名片假名<br />\n清音濁音呢啲基本結構先<br />\n唔洗背 我下堂會比練習大家做"},{"pid":"cf776fdd6805500607870aa41941052b2ae021fc","tid":2478003,"uid":246823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T15:38:22.000Z","msg":"例如<br />\n<br />\nか行ｘあ段 = か<br />\nさ行ｘい段 = し<br />\n<br />\n如此類推"},{"pid":"749051e99fe7913ffcae7b5cc81264db8af005b5","tid":2478003,"uid":246823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T15:47:13.000Z","msg":"清音<br />\n五十音既基本發音 唔加任可變化<br />\n<br />\n濁音<br />\nかさたは行加濁点&quot; 讀濁音<br />\n詳見上表<br />\n<br />\n半濁音<br />\nは行加半濁点&deg; 讀半濁音<br />\n<br />\n羅馬字 ローマ字<br />\n放便外國人讀同記五十音<br />\n唔洗背<br />\n<br />\n促音同長音之後再講"},{"pid":"c3009d4f1e5fe98af411556b3108c1b5fc8e020b","tid":2478003,"uid":26773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T18:48:55.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38973e4afb9ecec74fa5e6d81a723a2a38a73514","tid":2478003,"uid":336645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4fd87625ad5bcdc68db187bda8948cd8101df3e9","tid":2478003,"uid":170399,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T15:11:37.000Z","msg":"死蘇入黎未<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/cigar.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />等你出手"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T19:35:23.000Z","msg":"成功召喚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我竟然miss左呢個post"},{"pid":"cb5e921150338a219290ce6105c0d0778d002028","tid":2478003,"uid":336645,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T19:39:19.000Z","msg":"連登真係有好撚多人誤人子弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd6f98c289ab033c400458e09c5356250522bf4d","tid":2478003,"uid":214679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T19:42:34.000Z","msg":"教課書太死板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇啲系統性入腦速成方法？ <br />\n <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23a91ab7532d9b047f29a66a3339db23b1551ef4","tid":2478003,"uid":112386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T19:50:12.000Z","msg":"想學 以前上過